二十多尺的巨鳄都被活抓过
For God's sake, Jack, they've trapped crocs bigger than 20 feet.

986
01:01:09,590 --> 01:01:11,100
这并非不可能
This is not completely out of the question.

987
01:01:11,130 --> 01:01:12,440
你知道 这是可行的
It's possible, and you know that.

988
01:01:12,470 --> 01:01:16,730
你也知道佛州的人会杀死它
And those fucks from Florida won't even try, and you know that, too.

989
01:01:17,430 --> 01:01:21,030
我有麻醉药 他有一把大枪
I got the drugs. He's got a big cannon if anything goes wrong.

990
01:01:22,980 --> 01:01:24,450
该怎么引诱它?
How do you get him to the net?

991
01:01:24,480 --> 01:01:26,290
要毕太太叫它吗
Ask Mrs. Bickerman to call him?

992
01:01:26,320 --> 01:01:28,620
你们拿着麻醉枪站在卡车上
You guys can be in the trucks with the tranq guns.

993
01:01:28,650 --> 01:01:30,080
它一攻击就开车
If he charges, you take off.

994
01:01:30,110 --> 01:01:31,580
它跑不过你
He's not that fast.

995
01:01:32,740 --> 01:01:34,040
试一试无妨
We just have to try.

996
01:01:35,450 --> 01:01:39,000
只试一次就行
One try. Just one try.

997
01:01:40,200 --> 01:01:43,970
我们该怎么诱它上岸
Like Hank says, how would we lure him in?

998
01:01:44,790 --> 01:01:46,310
我会告你的
I'll sue you!

999
01:01:46,340 --> 01:01:47,430
尽管告
Go ahead.

1000
01:01:48,840 --> 01:01:51,190
你不能抢走我的牛
You can't take a cow by eminent domain!

1001
01:01:51,220 --> 01:01:52,980
当然能
We just did!

1002
01:01:53,010 --> 01:01:55,560
它不会受伤的
We won't let her get hurt, ma'am.

1003
01:01:55,590 --> 01:01:57,320
你们全是王八蛋
You're all cocksuckers!

1004
01:01:57,350 --> 01:02:00,150
我早就知道了
I knew at first. I just didn't want to say it.

1005
01:02:00,180 --> 01:02:02,400
我们很有把握
We know what we're doing.

1006
01:02:03,390 --> 01:02:06,110
牛被吊在直升机上
We got a cow hanging from a helicopter.

1007
01:02:08,110 --> 01:02:09,450
没什么风
Not much drag.

1008
01:02:09,480 --> 01:02:12,080
它不晃动就没事
As long as I can keep her from swinging, we're ok.

1009
01:02:20,620 --> 01:02:23,260
这么做是对的
We're doing the right thing.

1010
01:02:23,290 --> 01:02:25,840
等你进了鳄鱼肚就会后悔
You might feel different if you get eaten.

1011
01:02:25,870 --> 01:02:27,550
是啊 谢了
Yeah, thanks.

1012
01:02:39,510 --> 01:02:41,400
大家都有麻醉枪
Tranq gun with every rifle.

1013
01:02:41,430 --> 01:02:44,030
射程越远越好
That's as far back as it goes, right?

1014
01:02:53,320 --> 01:02:56,000
赫克托 别让牛下水
All right Hector, keep enough tension to hold her up.

1015
01:02:56,030 --> 01:02:58,250
谁知道它会不会游泳
We don't know how well she can swim.

1016
01:02:58,280 --> 01:02:59,790
是啊
Right.

1017
01:03:06,620 --> 01:03:08,220
我不想说
I hate to say it.

1018
01:03:08,250 --> 01:03:10,680
不过它越晃动越好
The more she thrashes, the better.

1019
01:03:11,550 --> 01:03:13,230
你们准备好了吗
You ready on shore?

1020
01:03:13,260 --> 01:03:15,430
我们准备好了
Yeah, we're all right. We're ready.

1021
01:03:16,010 --> 01:03:17,430
好了
Ok.

1022
01:03:19,760 --> 01:03:22,190
牛累了就把它拉上来
If she gets tired, pull her out.

1023
01:03:24,980 --> 01:03:27,160
它在干什么?
What's she doing now?

1024
01:03:27,190 --> 01:03:29,610
它想要飞
She's trying to fly.

1025
01:03:31,820 --> 01:03:34,490
这头牛很不爽
This is not a happy cow.

1026
01:03:35,320 --> 01:03:39,670
我希望巨鳄把你朋友全吃掉
I'm rooting for the crocodile. I hope he swallows your friends whole.

1027
01:03:39,700 --> 01:03:42,210
你尽管来逮捕我吧
You might want to arrest me for that, too.

1028
01:03:42,240 --> 01:03:46,880
希望警察被吃掉犯法吗
Is that a crime--To wish the chewing of law enforcement?

1029
01:03:46,910 --> 01:03:49,380
我不确定
I'm not sure, ma'am.

1030
01:03:51,000 --> 01:03:52,390
你抓到他了?
You got 'em?

1031
01:03:52,420 --> 01:03:53,720
这里
Yeah, over here.

1032
01:03:53,750 --> 01:03:55,730
在那儿
Little battery!

1033
01:03:55,760 --> 01:03:57,940
怎么回事
What's the deal?

1034
01:03:57,970 --> 01:03:59,770
我们试过了
Well, we tried.

1035
01:03:59,800 --> 01:04:02,650
再等一下子
Just a little longer, please.

1036
01:04:02,680 --> 01:04:04,780
它好像没在游泳
She doesn't seem to be swimming.

1037
01:04:04,810 --> 01:04:08,570
它像个大茶包被泡在水里
No, she's floating. She looks like a giant tea bag.

1038
01:04:09,480 --> 01:04:11,070
赫克托
Ok, Hector.

1039
01:04:11,100 --> 01:04:13,410
没有动静 没戏唱了
Good plan, bad bait. Game's up.

1040
01:04:13,440 --> 01:04:15,950
这头牛真令人失望
The cow disappoints me.

1041
01:04:17,990 --> 01:04:20,460
等一下
Hold on.

1042
01:04:20,490 --> 01:04:22,170
有动静了
I got something on the screen.

1043
01:04:22,200 --> 01:04:23,960
有什么
What do you got?

1044
01:04:23,990 --> 01:04:25,170
它来了
He's coming.

1045
01:04:25,200 --> 01:04:26,920
在哪儿
Where?

1046
01:04:26,950 --> 01:04:28,220
有多远
How far out?

1047
01:04:28,250 --> 01:04:29,340
大约三十米
30 meters or so.

1048
01:04:29,370 --> 01:04:31,850
它很慢 不过正游过来
He's moving slow, but he's definitely coming.

1049
01:04:31,880 --> 01:04:34,470
可以看到吗或只是雷达讯号
Can you confirm visually or just radar?

1050
01:04:34,500 --> 01:04:35,680
是雷达讯号
Radar.

1051
01:04:35,710 --> 01:04:39,020
它在水底但往这儿过来
He's underwater, but he is coming!

1052
01:04:39,050 --> 01:04:41,230
大伙儿上卡车
All right, everybody back in the trucks!

1053
01:04:41,260 --> 01:04:42,480
快点 快点
Move, move, move!

1054
01:04:42,510 --> 01:04:43,610
我们走 我们走
Let's go, let's go!

1055
01:04:43,640 --> 01:04:44,610
我们走
Let's go!

1056
01:04:44,640 --> 01:04:46,070
把它引过来
Lead him in.

1057
01:04:46,100 --> 01:04:47,980
来了
On our way.

1058
01:04:53,860 --> 01:04:56,750
大家要瞄准腹部和侧面
Remember to aim for the stomach and the sides!

1059
01:04:56,780 --> 01:04:59,870
麻醉针穿不过鳄背
These darts won't pierce his back!

1060
01:05:01,070 --> 01:05:04,000
它浮出来了
He's surfacing. There's his snout.

1061
01:05:04,280 --> 01:05:06,000
在那儿
There he is!

1062
01:05:06,030 --> 01:05:08,010
看到它了
We've spotted him, Hector.

1063
01:05:08,040 --> 01:05:10,130
你这小家伙
You little snacker.

1064
01:05:10,870 --> 01:05:13,140
太靠近就把牛拉起来
If he gets near her, pull up.

1065
01:05:13,170 --> 01:05:15,140
她担心牛的安全
She's worried about the cow now.

1066
01:05:16,420 --> 01:05:18,850
慢慢来
Nice and slow, Hector.

1067
01:05:20,630 --> 01:05:22,690
他的网子最好有用
This net thing better work.

1068
01:05:22,720 --> 01:05:24,270
你不是被网过吗
He got you with it.

1069
01:05:26,220 --> 01:05:29,110
它在水下四尺
We're in about 4 feet of water now.

1070
01:05:30,390 --> 01:05:31,660
它在叫耶
She's mooing.

1071
01:05:31,690 --> 01:05:33,370
你不会叫吗?
You wouldn't?

1072
01:05:33,400 --> 01:05:35,160
它也在乱踢
She's also kicking.

1073
01:05:37,480 --> 01:05:39,410
再靠近点
A little closer, Hector.

1074
01:05:49,120 --> 01:05:50,800
糟了
Oh, shit.

1075
01:05:56,130 --> 01:05:57,550
小心
Watch out!

1076
01:06:04,760 --> 01:06:06,230
王八蛋
Motherfucker!

1077
01:06:09,810 --> 01:06:11,650
可恶
Shit!

1078
01:06:11,680 --> 01:06:13,440
他人呢
Where is he?

1079
01:06:13,980 --> 01:06:15,950
我们得去救他
We gotta get to him.

1080
01:06:18,690 --> 01:06:20,000
支援我们
Back us up.

1081
01:06:20,030 --> 01:06:21,910
放下麻醉枪 用来福枪
Lose the tranq guns. go to the rifles.

1082
01:06:21,940 --> 01:06:24,330
用来福枪
Get the rifles!

1083
01:06:42,090 --> 01:06:43,100
它在哪里
Where'd he go?

1084
01:06:43,130 --> 01:06:44,060
等等
Hold up.

1085
01:06:44,090 --> 01:06:45,810
别下水
Don't go back into the water.

1086
01:06:45,840 --> 01:06:47,690
瞄准了就开枪
If you get a safe shot, take it.

1087
01:06:49,260 --> 01:06:51,650
赫克托 别动
Do not move, Hector!

1088
01:06:56,100 --> 01:06:58,330
你看到什么吗
Can you see anything from out there?

1089
01:06:58,360 --> 01:06:59,740
没有
Nothing!

1090
01:07:00,230 --> 01:07:02,410
也许它游走了
Maybe he swam back out!

1091
01:07:05,360 --> 01:07:06,460
天
Jesus!

1092
01:07:06,490 --> 01:07:07,620
赫克托
Hector!

1093
01:07:08,530 --> 01:07:09,920
嘿
Hey!

1094
01:07:09,950 --> 01:07:11,170
快回到卡车上
Get back in the truck!

1095
01:07:11,200 --> 01:07:12,380
我掩护他
I got him covered.

1096
01:07:19,460 --> 01:07:21,350
它在哪里
Where is he?

1097
01:07:21,380 --> 01:07:22,350
不知道
I don't know.

1098
01:07:22,380 --> 01:07:23,850
它潜到水底
He's gone under.

1099
01:07:34,100 --> 01:07:38,110
我现在觉得很安全
I just have this feeling everything's totally safe.

1100
01:07:42,070 --> 01:07:43,500
- 在那儿 - 它游走了
- There! - He's swimming out!

1101
01:07:43,530 --> 01:07:45,870
我看到它了 我看到它的尾巴
I think I see him! I think I see his tail!

1102
01:08:02,250 --> 01:08:03,930
糟了 凯莉
Shit! Kelly!

1103
01:08:22,310 --> 01:08:23,740
凯莉!
Kelly!

1104
01:08:33,870 --> 01:08:36,380
快游过来
Kelly, swim, swim to me!

1105
01:08:36,410 --> 01:08:38,210
快游到我这边
Swim to me, Kelly!

1106
01:08:41,710 --> 01:08:43,470
快开枪呀
Shoot the fucking thing!

1107
01:08:43,500 --> 01:08:45,800
我瞄不准
I don't have a clean shot.

1108
01:08:47,590 --> 01:08:48,770
潜下去
Dive under!

1109
01:08:48,800 --> 01:08:50,230
潜下去
Go under!

1110
01:08:54,680 --> 01:08:55,940
操
Fuck.

1111
01:09:17,160 --> 01:09:18,550
让我们来拯救它
"Let's save him."

1112
01:09:18,580 --> 01:09:20,210
活抓它真是烂点子
What a fucking great idea.

1113
01:09:48,320 --> 01:09:49,660
来
Come on.

1114
01:09:50,240 --> 01:09:51,660
来
Here.

1115
01:09:52,360 --> 01:09:54,330
上来
Here we go.

1116
01:09:55,030 --> 01:09:56,250
它在哪里
Where is he?

1117
01:09:56,280 --> 01:09:57,130
不知道
I don't know.

1118
01:09:57,160 --> 01:09:58,590
看不到它
We can't see him.

1119
01:09:59,620 --> 01:10:01,550
什么
What--What?

1120
01:10:06,920 --> 01:10:08,720
赫克托
Hector!

1121
01:10:22,980 --> 01:10:24,940
好吧
All right.

1122
01:10:25,190 --> 01:10:26,450
它玩完了
Game over.

1123
01:10:27,810 --> 01:10:29,200
看
Look.

1124
01:10:29,520 --> 01:10:31,410
它很痛苦
He's suffering.

1125
01:10:32,320 --> 01:10:34,420
我让它安乐死
I get to be humane.

1126
01:10:34,450 --> 01:10:36,170
不行...
No, no!

1127
01:10:36,200 --> 01:10:38,460
它被困住了
No, no, no, look, he's trapped!

1128
01:10:38,490 --> 01:10:40,130
我们成功了
We've done it!

1129
01:10:41,160 --> 01:10:43,470
不是被网住 不过它动不了
So what? It's not a net, but he's trapped.

1130
01:10:43,500 --> 01:10:44,760
任务完成
Mission accomplished.

1131
01:10:44,790 --> 01:10:45,800
杀死它
Shoot him.

1132
01:10:45,830 --> 01:10:47,100
我还有麻醉药 它半死不活
I got more drugs. He's half dead.

1133
01:10:47,130 --> 01:10:49,680
它还活着 开枪
He's half alive. Shoot him!

1134
01:11:04,520 --> 01:11:06,490
麻醉药生效了
The drugs are kicking in.

1135
01:11:30,420 --> 01:11:31,720
看看它
Look at him.

1136
01:11:31,750 --> 01:11:33,060
它完了
He's done.

1137
01:11:33,090 --> 01:11:34,600
汉克 开枪吧
Hank.

1138
01:11:34,630 --> 01:11:37,310
大家退后
All right, stand back.

1139
01:11:37,340 --> 01:11:39,350
不 警长
No, no, no, Sheriff I.

1140
01:11:39,590 --> 01:11:40,650
你看
Look.

1141
01:11:40,680 --> 01:11:41,730
你看 你看
Look, look.

1142
01:11:41,760 --> 01:11:42,820
它动弹不得
He's got nothing left.

1143
01:11:42,850 --> 01:11:45,070
向它开枪吧
Go ahead. Shoot him.

1144
01:11:54,320 --> 01:11:55,330
真的吗
Really?

1145
01:11:55,360 --> 01:11:57,170
- 杰克 我们... - 凯莉
- Jack, we don't-- - Kelly.

1146
01:11:57,200 --> 01:12:00,420
你不必杀死它 该死的 看看它
We don't have to destroy him! God damn it, look at him!

1147
01:12:05,000 --> 01:12:06,130
给我吧
Let me have that.

1148
01:12:06,160 --> 01:12:07,760
它被制伏了
He's been neutralized.

1149
01:12:07,790 --> 01:12:09,010
别这样 它被困住了
Come on, Jack, he's trapped!

1150
01:12:09,040 --> 01:12:10,180
看看它 它动也不能动
Look at him! He can't move!

1151
01:12:10,210 --> 01:12:11,930
- 看看它 - 何必杀它呢?
- Look at him! - What's the point?

1152
01:12:11,960 --> 01:12:13,430
你没必要杀它的
We don't have to do this.

1153
01:12:13,460 --> 01:12:15,100
求求你 别杀它
Jack, you don't have to. Please!

1154
01:12:30,730 --> 01:12:32,370
天啊
Oh, God!

1155
01:12:32,400 --> 01:12:34,080
我死定了
He's got me!

1156
01:12:34,110 --> 01:12:35,370
天啊
Jesus!

1157
01:12:35,400 --> 01:12:36,450
天啊
Jesus Christ!

1158
01:12:36,480 --> 01:12:39,620
有两只巨鳄
Are there 2? I think there's 2.

1159
01:12:39,650 --> 01:12:41,250
我看到了
I can see that.

1160
01:12:41,280 --> 01:12:42,790
它咬我
He bit me!

1161
01:12:42,820 --> 01:12:45,010
它咬我 有两只耶
He bit me! There's 2, there's 2!

1162
01:12:45,040 --> 01:12:46,290
我会数
I can count.

1163
01:12:48,200 --> 01:12:50,590
不
No!

1164
01:12:57,340 --> 01:12:58,680
又变成一只了
Back to one.

1165
01:13:01,970 --> 01:13:03,270
来吧
Go ahead.

1166
01:13:03,510 --> 01:13:04,770
绑起来
Flax him.

1167
01:13:14,270 --> 01:13:15,910
他们总算来了
Oh, here they are.

1168
01:13:15,940 --> 01:13:18,120
来的正是时候 你们好啊
Just in time. Nice to see you.

1169
01:13:27,660 --> 01:13:30,800
你们得替这只鳄鱼治伤
We're gonna need to get this reptile some medical attention.

1170
01:13:31,160 --> 01:13:35,510
我们用直升机困住它
We, uh...trapped him with our chopper.

1171
01:13:52,390 --> 01:13:53,320
波特兰
Portland?

1172
01:13:53,350 --> 01:13:54,570
对 到波特兰
Yes, Portland.

1173
01:13:54,600 --> 01:13:58,500
到那儿再想办法安置它
They'll tank him there until we figure out something better to do.

1174
01:13:58,530 --> 01:14:00,790
警长
So, Sheriff, Sheriff,

1175
01:14:00,820 --> 01:14:02,790
你轰掉巨鳄
you got to fire your big gun finally.

1176
01:14:02,820 --> 01:14:04,040
爽吗
Was it fun?

1177
01:14:04,950 --> 01:14:06,040
没那么爽
Overrated.

1178
01:14:06,070 --> 01:14:07,710
毕太太怎么说?
What'd Bickerman say?

1179
01:14:07,740 --> 01:14:10,970
她没说有两只巨鳄
Well, she didn't want to tell us about the second croc,

1180
01:14:11,000 --> 01:14:13,590
她怕我们会把它轰死
'cause she was afraid we'd blow its head off.

1181
01:14:13,620 --> 01:14:15,300
她猜得真准
Women's intuition.

1182
01:14:17,000 --> 01:14:18,180
还有空位
We got room for one more.

1183
01:14:18,210 --> 01:14:19,800
最好有人跟来
Someone should probably go with him.

1184
01:14:21,760 --> 01:14:24,650
我得收拾东西
I'm still packing up some stuff,

1185
01:14:24,680 --> 01:14:25,940
但是
but, uh...

1186
01:14:27,850 --> 01:14:29,440
我去吧
I'll go.

1187
01:14:29,470 --> 01:14:33,950
你一定得写报告
So, I imagine you're gonna have a few reports to do.

1188
01:14:33,980 --> 01:14:35,990
有需要尽管找我
If you need anything, let me know.

1189
01:14:36,020 --> 01:14:39,160
很高兴认识你
Yeah. It was nice meeting you.

1190
01:14:40,020 --> 01:14:43,080
别这么情绪化嘛
Gee, Hank, don't get all choked up.

1191
01:14:44,200 --> 01:14:45,920
我拿你还是没辄
With you, I'm still mixed.

1192
